<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6c275141-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s1971"><num value="1971">§ 1971.</num><heading> Definitions</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this subchapter:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id6c275142-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s1971/1"><num value="1" class="bold">(1)</num><heading class="bold"> Prize competition</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “prize competition” means the competition for the award of the Genius Prize for Save Our Seas Innovations established under <ref href="/us/usc/t33/s1972">section 1972 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id6c275143-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s1971/2"><num value="2" class="bold">(2)</num><heading class="bold"> Secretary</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “Secretary” means the Secretary of Commerce.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id6c275144-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/449/s121">Pub. L. 109–449, § 121</ref>, formerly <ref href="/us/pl/116/224/tI/s121">Pub. L. 116–224, title I, § 121</ref>, <date date="2020-12-18">Dec. 18, 2020</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/134/1081">134 Stat. 1081</ref>; renumbered <ref href="/us/pl/109/449/s121">Pub. L. 109–449, § 121</ref>, by <ref href="/us/pl/119/65/s4/a">Pub. L. 119–65, § 4(a)</ref>, <date date="2025-12-26">Dec. 26, 2025</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/139/1989">139 Stat. 1989</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
